               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="183606130174"></xptr>
               <p>and the prisoners were brought there with this property, of the prosecutor's, and these other two parcels.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Whitton.</hi> We saw the bundles on the ground in Marsh-gate-lane, and picked them up, but did not go away with them.</p>
               <p>(John Green, a shoemaker, of Parliament-court, Artillery-lane; and Richard Cas, deposed to Phillip's good character; and W. Holmes, a shoe-manufacturer, to that of Whitton's)</p>
